========================================
7. Lists in HTML
========================================

Ordered List:

<ol>
    <li>Apple</li>
    <li>Mango</li>
</ol>

Unordered List:

<ul>
    <li>Tea</li>
    <li>Coffee</li>
</ul>

Explanation:

<ol>
→ numbered list

<ul>
→ bullet list

<li>
→ list item

========================================
8. Links in HTML
========================================

