Visit Google
</a>

Explanation:

<a>
→ anchor tag

href
→ destination link

========================================
9. Images in HTML
========================================

<img src="image.jpg" alt="Nature Image">

Explanation:

src
→ image path

alt
→ alternative text

========================================
10. Tables in HTML
========================================

